com.thinkaurelius.titan.graphdb.query

Interface TitanPredicate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.function.BiPredicate<Object,Object>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Cmp, Contain, Geo, Text

    public interface TitanPredicate
extends java.util.function.BiPredicate<Object,Object>
    A special kind of BiPredicate which marks all the predicates that are natively supported by Titan and known to the query optimizer. Contains some custom methods that Titan needs for query answering and evaluation.

    This class contains a subclass used to convert Tinkerpop's BiPredicate implementations to the corresponding Titan predicates.
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
